      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『赤崎こころのいちばんカワイイTV』　こころ楽屋前",
      "startTime": 1.9266665242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃ～ん、おる？\nお誕生日のプレゼント持って来てんけど",
      "startTime": 6.3999998887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "（偶然同じテレビ局で収録やったからお祝いに来たけど）\n（楽屋、えらい静かやな……もうおらんのやろか）",
      "startTime": 14.862931109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "合言葉をどうぞ",
      "startTime": 19.6666670004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、合言葉……？　なんやそれ？\nうちやで！　うちうち！　うちやうち！",
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "うちうちうちうち言われても誰だか分からないです～！\n中に入る方は、合言葉を！　どうぞ！",
      "startTime": 34.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "合言葉、合言葉……王道なやつやと……\n「開け～ゴマ！」とか？",
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ぶっぶ～！　悪戯プランを極秘変更中なので合言葉を\n知らないスタッフさんは入れられず……すみません",
      "startTime": 51.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "（こころちゃん……さっき見た時はいつも通りやったけど）\n（これは内心、誕生日でめっちゃ浮かれとんな）",
      "startTime": 60.0333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "特別にもう一度だけチャンスをあげましょう！\n合言葉をどうぞ！　さあ！　合言葉を！！",
      "startTime": 67.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "すみません！　うちはスタッフさんやない、鈴村優や\n赤崎こころちゃんをお祝いに来たトリエルの鈴村優や！",
      "startTime": 75.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優ちゃん！？　すみません、すぐ開けます！",
      "startTime": 80.7000042755,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.995724499988,
          "startTime": 84.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9957244999905,
          "startTime": 84.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.662391199987,
          "startTime": 89.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、お誕生日おめでとう！\nはい、うちからのプレゼントは髪飾りや",
      "startTime": 89.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3799.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 93.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "おお～！　とっても可愛いです！　ハートに苺に\nキャンディー型まで！　沢山ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 98.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "番組収録の後に写真撮影があるのでその時に付けさせて\nもらいますね。ドッキリの最中に落としたら悲しいんで",
      "startTime": 106.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、誕生日にドッキリやるんや～\nあ、もしかして『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』？",
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　かくかくしかじかで、急遽プランE～Xまでの\n追加悪戯を仕掛けることになりバタバタしてたんです～",
      "startTime": 123.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そうやったんや。だから悪戯内容がバレんように\n合言葉を設定しとったってことか。理解したわ",
      "startTime": 131.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "その通りです！　決してこころが誕生日だからって\n浮かれてた訳ではありませんからね！",
      "startTime": 139.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんな～、浮かれてるんかと思っとったわ\nところで、合言葉はなんやったん？",
      "startTime": 147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "『この頃こころ、ゴロゴロこころコロコロこころ』\n……莉央さんが寝言で言ってた心無～い言葉です",
      "startTime": 153.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、おもろい寝言やな～。莉央さんが\nどんな夢見とったんかめっちゃ気になるわ",
      "startTime": 161.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "全然面白くないです！　ま、まあ？　夢に見るくらい\n莉央さんはこころのことが大好きなんでしょうけど～",
      "startTime": 170.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11133.333333400004,
          "startTime": 181.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すみません！　そろそろ生放送始まっちゃうんで\nスタジオ向かいます！　プレゼントありがとうです！",
      "startTime": 177.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_53_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "（ふふっ、可愛いな～こころちゃん。廊下をスキップ）\n（してんのに浮かれてへんってのはちょっと無理あるで）",
      "startTime": 187.6000101725,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}